{"title":"微信小程序-什么是WXML","date":"2023-04-08T04:02:26.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 8, 2023","L":"04/08/2023","MM-DD":"04-08"},"link":"2023/04/08/Web/微信小程序/wxml/16-微信小程序-什么是WXML","tags":["微信小程序"],"updated":"2023-04-08T04:31:16.883Z","content":"<h1 id=\"什么是wxml\">什么是WXML<a title=\"#什么是wxml\" href=\"#什么是wxml\"></a></h1>\n<p>WXML（WeiXin Markup Language）是框架设计的一套标签语言，类似于HTML，结合<a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/component/\" target=\"_blank\">基础组件</a>、<a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/framework/view/wxml/event.html\" target=\"_blank\">事件系统</a>，可以构建出页面的结构。</p>\n<p>要完整了解 WXML 语法，请参考<a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/reference/wxml/\" target=\"_blank\">WXML 语法参考</a>。</p>\n<h1 id=\"特点\">特点<a title=\"#特点\" href=\"#特点\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>严格区分大小写</li>\n</ul>\n<p>正确示例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span>严格区分大小写<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>错误示例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">Text</span>&gt;</span>严格区分大小写<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img2023.cnblogs.com/blog/2105804/202304/2105804-20230408122858877-321943298.png\" alt=\"image-20230408122858001\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>必须严格闭合，否则会报错</li>\n</ul>\n<p>正确示例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span>必须严格闭合<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>错误示例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img2023.cnblogs.com/blog/2105804/202304/2105804-20230408123024704-1019906219.png\" alt=\"image-20230408123023915\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"微信小程序-WXML数据绑定","link":"2023/04/08/Web/微信小程序/wxml/17-微信小程序-WXML数据绑定"},"next":{"title":"微信小程序-新增RPX响应式单位","link":"2023/04/06/Web/微信小程序/wxss/15-微信小程序-新增RPX响应式单位"},"plink":"http://example.com/2023/04/08/Web/微信小程序/wxml/16-微信小程序-什么是WXML/","toc":[{"id":"什么是wxml","title":"什么是WXML","index":"1"},{"id":"特点","title":"特点","index":"2"}],"reading_time":"153 words in 1 min"}